name: ingotink_minting_dapp
description: The narrative of this project is to engrave INGOTINK into stone. Reflecting timeless ancient Roman and Greek statues of hierarchy clashing between pop art culture. Displayed digitally the projects essence resembles tradition vs futurism. Enduring the spirituality and philosophy of the past and present. Conforming from European empires to decentralized web3. INGOTINK Welcomes you to Forever.
author: Eki Bagas, Daniel Eugene Botha
